definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in West Lindsey district, Lincolnshire , England ( OS grid ref TF0792 ) .
A locality in Lenton, Keisby and Osgodby parish, South Kesteven district, Lincolnshire ( OS grid ref TF0228 ) .
A village and civil parish in North Yorkshire , England , previously in Scarborough district ( OS grid ref TA0584 ) .
A locality in Thirkleby High and Low with Osgodby parish, North Yorkshire , previously in Hambleton district ( OS grid ref SE4980 ) .
A village in Barlby with Osgodby parish, North Yorkshire , previously in Selby district ( OS grid ref SE6433 ) .
